### BACKGROUND

The Grantor is the sole owner and inventor of the intellectual property
described below, protected under the Restricted Truth Preservation License
(RTPL) v1.0, which prohibits all use by any person or entity except under
conditions specified by the Grantor.

This instrument creates a named carve-out from the RTPL exclusively for
BrockBox LLC. **All restrictions of the RTPL remain fully in force for all
other parties.** This grant does not constitute a general public license
and does not waive the Grantor's rights against any third party.

---

### SCOPE OF GRANT

